description._content: Description: Wedding Group (L. to R.) Pastor Ferris; Irma Warren (single, mother of 1); Caius Christian; Joyce Young, bride (spinster, mother of 3); Radley Christian, bridegroom; "Trinity" Young; Jacob Warren. Location: Pitcairn Islands, Pitcairn Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: The Church Officers. (Front Row L. to R.) Fred. Christian; Flora Christian (his wife); Mrs. Ferris; Mr. Ferris; Willie Christian; Agnes Ross (New Zealander); Roy Clark. (Back Row) Clarence Young; Oliver Clark; Langford Warren; Wilson Young; Anderson Warren; Len. Brown; Oscar Clark; Bert Christian; Ben. Christian. Location: Pitcairn Islands, Pitcairn Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: A group of Islanders at the Wedding on 10/11/53. Warren Christian, late C.M. of doubtful fame - arrowed. Location: Pitcairn Islands, Pitcairn Islands Date: 10 November 1953 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/641.
